🎨 Pretty Print JSON

Use `indent` for readable formatting.

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

💻 Example

```python id="pretty_json"
import json

student = {
    "name": "Saakshi",
    "age": 22,
    "course": "Python"
}

print(
    json.dumps(
        student,
        indent=4
    )
)
```

---

▶️ Output

```json id="pretty_output"
{
    "name": "Saakshi",
    "age": 22,
    "course": "Python"
}
```

---

🔑 Sort JSON Keys

---

💻 Example

```python id="sort_keys"
